metadata.name: Football love
metadata.description:
''Living standards in mountain villages, which have been deprived of many opportunities for years, are very difficult. In difficult conditions of life, children are always children. Despite these difficult conditions, people did not leave their villages and raised their children in these difficult conditions. The greatest entertainment of children is of course football, as in the whole world''
